# Scratchpad

## Current task
Second whole-repo adversarial hardening pass — COMPLETE

## Plan
- [X] Baseline full tests, Ruff, TypeScript build, shell syntax
- [X] Independent audits: auth/persistence, routing/upstream, frontend/deploy
